@Mod_Brandon12111 wrote:

#1 Client-Sided, GUI.Java change the IP of the server to 127.0.0.1 (As you’re the localhost)
#2 Open Z-FileSearcher and type in the Old IP to see if it’s anywhere else in the client Classes etc.
#3 Make sure the Compiler has your right JDK version in it.
#4 Compile
#5 Run.bat

There you go (: If this doesn’t work please reply to this
